name: ZEG SPIEDER #SD01
description:
When an alien virus infected the world humans and machines bonded. We escaped into the virtual world to fight for our existence. This is new URTH an original series featuring an array of original characters. Zeg Spieder is an abomination. Using human, spider, and alien DNA, the horde has created their first in a series of nightmare children. 
This is a special character edition not available for purchase and is a gift from me to those early adopters of my URTH series. An official release version of Zeg will be available in the near future.
